dialog.body: Hello! Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Daniel Brown. May I have your name, please?
Hello, Daniel. This is Linda Hall.
Nice to meet you, Linda. How can I assist you today?
I need to file a new claim for a recent accident.
I'm sorry to hear that, Linda. To start the process, I'll need some information. Could you please provide me with the date of the accident?
The accident happened on two five zero eight two zero two one.
Thank you, Linda. Could you also confirm the location where the accident took place?
The accident occurred at five zero zero Main Street, Cityville.
Great. Thank you for providing that information. I will initiate the claim process for you. Is there anything else I can assist you with today, Linda?
No, that's all for now, thank you, Daniel.
You're welcome, Linda. Thank you for reaching out to us. Have a great day!
